+*Auditor*
+
+```sql
+CREATE SHARDING AUDITOR sharding_key_required_auditor (
+TYPE(NAME="DML_SHARDING_CONDITIONS")
+);
+
+ALTER SHARDING AUDITOR sharding_key_required_auditor (
+TYPE(NAME="DML_SHARDING_CONDITIONS")
+);
+
+DROP SHARDING AUDITOR IF EXISTS sharding_key_required_auditor;
+```
