 *Auto Table*
 ```sql
 CREATE SHARDING TABLE RULE t_order (
 RESOURCES(resource_0,resource_1),
 SHARDING_COLUMN=order_id,TYPE(NAME="hash_mod",PROPERTIES("sharding-count"="4")),
